to see the current state:

- my player-info
 - resources
- all the playing pieces (on all locations)
- the board
    - the tiles
        - the planets

- the game history
    - all previous turns
        - all previous orders and their resolutions
- my currently active orders
- game settings
    - the piece types
    - the order types

to assign orders:

- the tactical order
    - pick ships to move to that location
    - pick new vessels to build here
    - pick which planets to invade
    - move contained pieces to other containers

to actually move the turn:

- resolve all tactical orders
- resolve all battles
- resolve all invasions
- recalculate available resources

to start a new game:

- generate a board
- assign players
- set starting units